Returns `None` if the pointer is null, or else returns a shared reference to the value wrapped in `Some`. If the value may be uninitialized, [`as_uninit_ref`](about:blank/primitive.pointer.html#method.as_uninit_ref-1 "primitive pointer") must be used instead.

